flowchart TD
  subgraph User Authentication & Usage
    A1[Client sends API Key] --> A2{Valid API Key?}
    A2 -- No --> A3[Reject Request]
    A2 -- Yes --> A4[Authenticate Bearer Token]
    A4 --> A5{Token Valid?}
    A5 -- No --> A3
    A5 -- Yes --> A6[Check Monthly Usage Limit]
    A6 -- Exceeded --> A7[Reject Request - Limit Hit]
    A6 -- Ok --> A8[Proceed With API Request]
  end

  subgraph Menu Management
    M1[Create Menu Item] --> M2[Save Item]
    M3[List Menu Items] --> M4[Return Items List]
    M5[Update Menu Item] --> M2
    M6[Delete Menu Item] --> M7[Remove Item]
  end

  subgraph Order Processing
    O1[Place New Order] --> O2[Validate Order Items]
    O2 --> O3[Calculate Total]
    O3 --> O4[Save Order in DB]
    O4 --> O5[Generate Print Jobs]
  end

  subgraph Print Management
    P1[Register Printer] --> P2[Save Printer Info]
    P3[Create/Update Print Template] --> P4[Save Template]
    
    O5 --> P5[Assign Print Jobs to Printers with Templates]
    P5 --> P6[Add Jobs to Print Queue]
    P7[Printer Fetches Pending Jobs] --> P8[Print Content Using Template]
    P8 --> P9[Update Job Status: Printing]
    P9 --> P10[Update Job Status: Completed or Failed]
  end

  subgraph Payment Management
    Pay1[Record Payment] --> Pay2[Validate Payment]
    Pay2 --> Pay3[Save Payment Info]
    Pay3 --> Pay4[Update Order Payment Status]
  end

  subgraph Employee Management
    E1[Add Employee] --> E2[Save Employee Details]
    E3[List Employees] --> E4[Return Employees List]
  end

  subgraph Customer Copy Workflow
    O4 --> C1[Create Customer Copy Print Job]
    C1 --> P5
  end

  %% Link main flow
  A8 -->|Item APIs| M1
  A8 --> M3
  A8 -->|Order APIs| O1
  A8 -->|Payment APIs| Pay1
  A8 -->|Employee APIs| E1
  A8 --> E3
  A8 -->|Printer APIs| P1
  A8 -->|Template APIs| P3
  A8 -->|Print Jobs APIs| P7
